{"tid":396401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺大民主牆捍衛言論自由語遭撕去 警方到場調查","createTime":"2017-09-11T15:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T16:33:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"652442b0273ce46b06945c681a46b33e3a0f9f77","tid":396401,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"大學校園港獨標語風波延伸至嶺南大學！晚上約9時，嶺大校園內學生會民主牆上，28個表達捍衛言論自由的語句，疑遭人惡意破壞撕去，警方接報到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n該28個字的語句，原本以每張A4紙各印一個字，貼在民主牆上，表達：「你不主張香港獨立，亦應捍衛言論自由，縱然立場不同，但應互相尊重」，但結果被人撕掉。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170911/large/1505136996_9078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F1505136996_9078.jpg&h=d80f0a0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4575a162f50745fa13298af7048ada9083d68270","tid":396401,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20170911_20170911-221652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20170911_20170911-221652.jpg&h=01dda0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20170911_20170911-230541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20170911_20170911-230541.jpg&h=29359bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20170911_20170911-231713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20170911_20170911-231713.jpg&h=e4fcd61b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fcf7cba46811ae23446b4070a4cf440399c5667","tid":396401,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1775c520fbfb684baffd7a6622206f3b94ae